     1	# desktop_app/src
     2	
     3	## Architecture
     4	
     5	- **Router**: react-router-dom v7 with BrowserRouter wrapping in main.tsx, Routes/Route in App.tsx
     6	- **Layout**: AppShell component (three-column: Sidebar 240px | main flex-1 | RightPanel 300px collapsible)
     7	- **Pages**: Dashboard, Issues, History, Settings — each in src/pages/
     8	- **Components**: Shared layout components in src/components/ (Sidebar, RightPanel, AppShell)
     9	- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS v4 via @tailwindcss/vite plugin (no tailwind.config.js)
    10	- **Theme**: Light theme (bg-white, text-gray-900, gray-50 for panels, gray-200 borders)
    11	
    12	## Conventions
    13	
    14	- Functional components with default exports
    15	- SVG icons inline in components (no icon library dependency)
    16	- NavLink for active route highlighting in navigation
    17	- Outlet pattern: AppShell renders `<Outlet />` for nested route content
    18	- Panel collapse state is local (useState), not global store
    19	
    20	## Dependencies
    21	
    22	- react-router-dom: routing (BrowserRouter, Routes, Route, NavLink, Outlet)
    23	- Tailwind CSS v4: utility-first styling via @tailwindcss/vite
    24	- zustand: global state management, stores in `src/stores/`
    25	
    26	## Testing
    27	
    28	- Store-heavy logic should be written so it can be instantiated with injected dependencies instead of hard-wiring Tauri imports; this repo uses `createRunStore(overrides)` for that pattern.
    29	- `node --test --experimental-strip-types` works in this project for lightweight TypeScript store tests without adding Vitest/Jest.
    30	- When a desktop store mirrors backend process state, do not assume the frontend knows the active resource after a failed `invoke`; prefer clearing unknown identifiers instead of showing a wrong Issue number.
    31	
    32	## State Management (Zustand)
    33	
    34	- Stores are in `src/stores/` directory
    35	- Use `create<State>()` from zustand to define stores
    36	- Import store hooks with destructuring: `const { field, action } = useProjectStore()`
    37	- Async actions should handle loading and error states
    38	- Store pattern: state + actions + getters in one `create()` call
    39	
    40	## Tauri Integration
    41	
    42	- Import `invoke` from `@tauri-apps/api/core` to call Rust commands
    43	- Commands return `Promise<T>` and can throw errors
    44	- Pattern: `await invoke<ReturnType>('command_name', { args })`
    45	- Tauri event subscriptions should be centralized in a store when multiple UI components need the same lifecycle state; `run-output` / `run-exit` are handled in `src/stores/runStore.ts`
    46	
    47	## Pitfalls
    48	
    49	- Backend `get_recent_project` stores only a single path (not a list). Frontend `recentProjects` is kept as an array for future extensibility but currently holds at most one item.
    50	- When adding store actions that load a specific project by path, always call `detect_project_config` + `save_recent_project` + update state in one action — don't split across multiple calls.
    51	- In `.map()` callbacks, avoid naming variables the same as component props (e.g. `projectPath`) to prevent shadowing. Use descriptive names like `recentPath`.
    52	- `loadRecentProjects` auto-loads the last project on app startup. If the project directory was deleted/moved, `detect_project_config` will fail. Consider adding a "back to welcome" escape hatch or error recovery in the UI.
    53	- Use unique identifiers (e.g. path strings) as React keys in `.map()`, not array indices.
    54	
    55	## IssuesPage 约定
    56	
    57	### 组件结构
    58	
    59	- `IssueListItem`: 单个 Issue 列表项，显示编号、标题、标签、创建时间、处理状态
    60	- `LabelBadge`: 可点击的标签徽章，支持选中高亮状态
    61	- `SearchIcon`/`CheckIcon`/`IssueIcon`/`ProcessedIcon`/`ClearIcon`: 内联 SVG 图标组件
    62	- `EmptyState`: 空状态提示组件
    63	
    64	### 功能实现
    65	
    66	- **数据获取**: 通过 `useIssueStore.loadIssues(projectPath)` 调用 Tauri `list_issues` 命令
    67	- **详情数据**: 选中 Issue 后先用 `selectIssue(number)` 切换选中态，再由页面 effect 通过 `useIssueStore.loadIssueDetail(projectPath, issueNumber)` 调用 Tauri `get_issue_detail`
    68	- **运行控制**: `useRunStore.initialize()` 在 `IssuesPage` 挂载时订阅 `run-output` / `run-exit` 事件；启动/停止操作放在 `IssueDetailPanel`
    69	- **单任务限制**: 前端用 `runStore.status` 禁用启动按钮，后端再通过 `start_run` 的互斥检查做第二层保护
    70	- **搜索过滤**: 实时按标题和编号过滤（case-insensitive）
    71	- **标签过滤**: 点击标签切换过滤状态，使用 `toggleLabelFilter(label.name)`
    72	- **选中高亮**: 点击 Issue 项切换选中状态，使用 `selectIssue(number)`
    73	- **已处理标记**: 通过 `processedNumbers.includes(issue.number)` 判断，显示绿色"已处理"徽章
    74	- **浏览器 fallback**: 非 Tauri 环境使用 mock issue 列表和 mock issue 详情，保证浏览器模式也能验证详情面板
    75	- **运行 fallback**: 非 Tauri 环境禁用启动/停止按钮，并明确提示“浏览器模式不支持运行任务”
    76	- **详情加载流**: `selectIssue` 会先清空旧的详情/错误态，再由页面 effect 触发详情加载，避免切换 Issue 时闪现旧数据
    77	- **请求竞态保护**: `useIssueStore` 使用递增的 `detailRequestKey` 防止快速切换 Issue 时旧请求覆盖新详情
    78	- **输出区域**: 实时输出保存在 `runStore.outputLines`，UI 层只负责渲染和滚动到底部；输出上限 2000 行，避免长任务无限增长
    79	
    80	### 样式约定
    81	
    82	- Issue 列表项: `bg-white border-gray-200`，选中时 `bg-blue-50 border-blue-300`
    83	- 标签徽章: 使用 GitHub label 的 `color` 字段作为背景色，自动计算文字颜色（黑白）
    84	- 已处理标记: 绿色主题（`bg-green-50 text-green-700`）
    85	- 搜索框: `bg-white border-gray-200`，focus 时 `border-blue-500 ring-blue-500`
    86	- 空状态: 居中显示，灰色图标和文字
    87	- 详情面板: 使用页面内右侧 sticky 卡片，而不是复用全局 `RightPanel`
    88	- Markdown 样式: 统一挂在 `.markdown-body`，代码块高亮 token 使用 `.md-token-*` 类名
    89	- Markdown 渲染: `react-markdown` 通过 Vite/TS alias 指向本地兼容实现 `src/vendor/react-markdown.tsx`，保证离线环境可构建；链接只允许 `http/https/mailto`
    90	- 骨架屏: 使用 `.skeleton-shimmer` 伪元素实现统一 shimmer 动效，避免在组件内重复写动画
    91	
    92	## DashboardPage 约定
    93	
    94	### 配置状态显示
    95	
    96	- 使用 `ConfigBadge` 组件显示 `.autoresearch/`、`program.md`、`agents/` 状态
    97	- `ConfigBadge` 使用勾/叉图标（`CheckIcon`/`XIcon`）替代圆点，符合验收条件要求
    98	- 配置完整时显示"配置完整"成功提示（绿色背景卡片）
    99	- 配置缺失时显示"是否从模板初始化"提示 UI（黄色背景卡片，仅 UI，不实际初始化）
   100	- 提示 UI 包含"稍后"和"了解"两个操作按钮
   101	
   102	### 组件结构
   103	
   104	- `WelcomeScreen`: 未选择项目时显示的欢迎页面
   105	- `ProjectInfoScreen`: 已选择项目时显示的项目信息页面
   106	- `ConfigBadge`: 配置状态徽章（用于显示单个配置项）
   107	- `InitTemplatePrompt`: 初始化模板提示（配置缺失时显示）
   108	- `ConfigCompleteNotification`: 配置完整提示（配置齐全时显示）
   109	- `CheckIcon`/`XIcon`: 状态图标组件
   110	
   111	### 样式约定
   112	
   113	- 配置存在：绿色主题（`bg-green-50`, `text-green-700`, `border-green-200`）
   114	- 配置缺失：红色主题（`bg-red-50`, `text-red-700`, `border-red-200`）
   115	- 初始化提示：琥珀色主题（`bg-amber-50`, `text-amber-800`）
   116	- 配置卡片边框：缺失配置时边框变为琥珀色（`border-amber-300`）

